The returned array must not be null.
The length of the returned array must be equal to the length of the input array "nums".
The returned array must be in the form [x1, y1, x2, y2, ..., xn, yn].
The elements in the returned array must be shuffled in a random order.
The first half of the elements in the returned array must be the first half of the elements in the input array "nums".
The second half of the elements in the returned array must be the second half of the elements in the input array "nums".
The order of the elements within each half of the returned array must be the same as the order of the elements within each half of the input array "nums".
